om | accessdate=April 19, 2015}}</ref>\n! Budget\n! Box office<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=mattreeves.htm | title=Matt Reeves Movie Box office | publisher=[[Amazon.com]] | work=boxofficemojo.com | accessdate=April 19, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[The Pallbearer]]'' || 45% (20 reviews)<ref>[[Rotten Tomatoes]], \"[http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pallbearer/ The Pallbearer (1996)]\". Accessed December 25, 2014.</ref> || {{N/A}} || {{N/A}} || $5 million || $7.65 million<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=pallbearer.htm|title=The Pallbearer (1996) - Box Office Mojo|publisher=[[Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2010-02-12}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Cloverfield]]'' || 77% (204 reviews) || 64 (37 reviews) || C || $25 million || $170.8 million\n|-\n| ''[[Let Me In (film)|Let Me In]]'' || 88% (226 reviews) || 79 (35 reviews) || C+ || $20 million || $24.1 million\n|-\n| ''[[Dawn of the Planet of the Apes]]'' || 91% (306 reviews) || 79 (48 reviews) || A\u2013 || $170 million || $710.6 million\n|-\n| ''[[War for the Planet of the Apes]]'' || 94% (343 reviews) || 82 (50 reviews) || A\u2013 || $150 million || $490.7 million\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n* {{IMDb name}}\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20111001210105/http://laist.com/2008/01/09/laist_interview_88.php LAist.com Interview with Matt Reeves]\n{{Matt Reeves}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Reeves, Matt}}\n[[Category:1966 births]]\n[[Category:American film directors]]\n[[Category:Film producers from New York (state)]]\n[[Category:American male screenwriters]]\n[[Category:American soap opera writers]]\n[[Category:American television directors]]\n[[Category:Television producers from New York (state)]]\n[[Category:American television writers]]\n[[Category:Science fiction film directors]]\n[[Category:Horror film directors]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Rockville Centre, New York]]\n[[C